fields.name: Onyx Sugar Skull Blend
fields.notes: This coffee was bright and balanced. More flavor than other coffees. Would like to try it 1 coarser next time.

fields.name: Barista Parlor Gold Mountain Cascara
fields.notes: This coffee was yummy. I had notes of papaya and pecan.  Balanced and bright. I don’t think the settings need any adjusting.

fields.name: Counter Culture Fast Forward
fields.notes: This coffee was nutty and had a medium mouthfeel. It was good but slightly watery. I’ll adjust on my next to be a little finer.
